description:
Extra Clean, CARFAX 1-Owner, LOW MILES - 8,429! 3LT trim. Heated/Cooled Leather Seats, NAV, Alloy Wheels, Dual Zone A/C, Remote Engine Start, Onboard Communications System, Satellite Radio, Premium Sound System, Back-Up Camera.

KEY FEATURES INCLUDE
Heated Driver Seat, Cooled Driver Seat, Back-Up Camera, Premium Sound System, Satellite Radio, Onboard Communications System, Chrome Wheels, Remote Engine Start, Dual Zone A/C, WiFi Hotspot, Cross-Traffic Alert, Blind Spot Monitor, Heated Seats, Heated/Cooled Seats. Remote Trunk Release, Keyless Entry, Electronic Stability Control, Heated Mirrors, Bucket Seats. Chevrolet 3LT with White Pearl Metallic Tricoat exterior and Ceramic White with Red stitching interior features a 8 Cylinder Engine with 490 HP at 6450 RPM*.

OPTION PACKAGES
Z51 PERFORMANCE PACKAGE includes (J55) Z51 performance brakes, (FE3) Z51 performance suspension, (NPP) performance exhaust, (GM7) performance rear axle ratio, (G96) Electronic Limited Slip Differential (eLSD), (T0A) Z51 rear spoiler, front splitter, (XFQ) 245/35ZR19 front and 305/30ZR20 rear, blackwall, high performance tires and (V08) heavy-duty cooling system, 70TH ANNIVERSARY SPECIAL EDITION includes (Q9A) 19 front/20 rear 20-spoke Midnight Gray forged aluminum wheels with Red stripe, (J6N) Edge Red-painted calipers, (VTB) Rear fascia/roof storage protector in Black with embroidered crossed flags logo, LPO, (HV1) Ceramic White leather seating surfaces with Red stitching, (3F9) Torch Red seat belt color, 70th anniversary exterior badging and logo on wheel caps, seats, steering wheel and sill plates, and unique VIN sequence Includes (J6N) Edge Red-painted calipers or (J6F) Bright Red-painted calipers are available to order. SUSPENSION, Z51 PERFORMANCE WITH MAGNETIC SELECTIVE RIDE CONTROL includes (B4Z) Performance Traction Management, CONVERTIBLE TOP, CARBON FLASH-PAINTED NACELLES AND ROOF, AUDIO SYSTEM, CHEVROLET INFOTAINMENT 3 PREMIUM SYSTEM WITH CONNECTED NAVIGATION 8 diagonal HD color touchscreen, AM/FM stereo, Bluetooth® audio streaming for 2 active devices, Apple CarPlay® and Android Auto® capable, enhanced voice recognition, additional memory for in-vehicle apps, cloud connected personalization for select infotainment and vehicle settings. (STD), ENGINE, 6.2L V8 DI, HIGH-OUTPUT Variable Valve Timing (VVT), Active Fuel Management (AFM) (490 hp [365.4 kW] @ 6450 rpm, 465 lb-ft of torque [627.8 N-m] @ 5150 rpm) (STD), TRANSMISSION, 8-SPEED DUAL CLUTCH, INCLUDES MANUAL AND AUTO MODES (STD). Serviced here, Locally owned and traded here!

SHOP WITH CONFIDENCE
Extra Clean

WHO WE ARE
We are a member of the Hendrick Automotive Group, the 6th largest automotive group in the United States. This gives us many advantages over our competition. All of our pre-owned vehicles have gone through a rigorous inspection process for your peace of mind.

description:
Discover the ultimate in power, capability, and comfort with this exceptional 2024 Ford F-350SD Platinum. Boasting a robust 6.7L High Output Power Stroke V8 Diesel engine and 10-Speed Automatic transmission, this 4WD behemoth is ready to tackle any task with unparalleled strength and efficiency.

CLEAN CARFAX NO ACCIDENTS
CARFAX ONE OWNER
6.7L V8 Diesel Turbocharged (Power Stroke) with High Output, Manual Push-Button Engine-Exhaust Braking, 48 Gallon Fuel Tank, GVWR: 11,500 lb Payload Package and 3.31 Axle Ratio
Tough Bed Spray-In Bedliner
5th Wheel/Gooseneck Hitch Prep Package
FX4 Off-Road Package with Hill Descent Control, Off-Road Specifically Tuned Shock Absorbers, and Unique FX4 Off-Road Box Decal
Electronic-Locking w/3.31 Axle Ratio
Max Recline Seats with 10-way power driver and 8-way power passenger

This meticulously maintained Platinum trim level F-350SD offers a host of premium features that elevate the driving experience. Enjoy the convenience of the Connected Navigation system, the exceptional sound quality of the B&O Unleashed Sound System, and the added confidence of advanced safety technologies like Blind Spot Monitoring and Rear Cross-Traffic Alert.

Whether you're tackling tough job sites, towing heavy loads, or embarking on off-road adventures, this Ford F-350SD Platinum is ready to rise to the challenge. The FX4 Off-Road Package equips this behemoth with the necessary tools to conquer even the most demanding terrain, while the Gooseneck Hitch Kit provides the ultimate in towing capability.

As a Ford Gold Certified pre-owned vehicle, this F-350SD Platinum comes with a comprehensive 172-point inspection, Roadside Assistance, and a transferable warranty that provides peace of mind. Additionally, you'll receive 22,000 FordPass Rewards Points to use towards your first two maintenance visits, ensuring a seamless ownership experience.

Experience the power, capability, and refinement of this exceptional 2024 Ford F-350SD Platinum. Visit our showroom today and let us demonstrate how this remarkable truck can transform your driving and towing needs.
